comment:
1) Schedule F carries the risk of unwarranted intrusion on merit-based review of science thereby limiting the ability to conduct science without bias.
2) Peer review for NIH & other agencies is mandated by federal law;
3) Program officers at NIH, DOD, NSF & other agencies should not become Schedule F employees.

